room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Plano in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_address: 2301 N Central Expy, Suite 285 Plano, TX 75075
room_description: You wake up handcuffed and blindfolded in a strange room and realize you have been kidnapped! Joined by several other victims, you discover clues hidden throughout the room. Can your team work together and find a way to escape? Time is running out and the kidnapper will return soon!
